      a: "Create unlimited sponsor tiers — Platinum, Gold, Silver, or custom levels — each with defined benefits like logo placement, booth size, speaking slots, and lead capture access."
    },
    {
      q: "Is attendee data secure and audit-ready?",
      a: "Yes. All data is encrypted at rest and in transit. Role-based access controls, audit logs, and data export policies help meet financial services compliance requirements."
    },
    {
      q: "Can AI match investors with startups at fintech events?",
      a: "Yes. AI Smart-Connect analyzes investor preferences and startup profiles to suggest relevant matches. Participants can schedule structured 1:1 meetings directly through the platform."
    }
  ]}
  supportNote={{ title: "Free finance event consultation", desc: "Our team helps you configure secure registration, VIP management, and sponsor workflows for your financial services event." }}
  supportCta={{ label: "Plan my finance event", href: "/book-a-demo/" }}
/>
